description: Welcome home to one of the best kept secrets in Midtown. Steps to Piedmont Park, and Colony Square shopping/restaurant complex. Gated off-street parking with two dedicated spaces. Well-appointed 2 bedroom/2 bathroom condo with hardwood floors, walk-in closets. End unit with tons of natural light. Laundry in unit. Stone countertops, plenty of cabinet space. Brand new paint throughout the unit. Come see this gem of a home today!
